{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":43000,"text":"[Sanskrit]"},{"time":50000,"text":"This is an ode to the mother goddess,"},{"time":52000,"text":"that most of us in India learn when we are children."},{"time":58000,"text":"I learned it when I was four"},{"time":60000,"text":"at my mother's knee."},{"time":65000,"text":"That year she introduced me to dance,"},{"time":68000,"text":"and thus began"},{"time":70000,"text":"my tryst with classical dance."},{"time":73000,"text":"Since then -- it's been four decades now --"},{"time":77000,"text":"I've trained with the best in the field,"},{"time":79000,"text":"performed across the globe,"},{"time":81000,"text":"taught young and old alike,"},{"time":84000,"text":"created, collaborated,"},{"time":86000,"text":"choreographed,"},{"time":88000,"text":"and wove a rich tapestry"},{"time":90000,"text":"of artistry, achievement and awards."},{"time":94000,"text":"The crowning glory was in 2007,"},{"time":97000,"text":"when I received this country's"},{"time":99000,"text":"fourth highest civilian award, the Padma Shri,"},{"time":101000,"text":"for my contribution to art."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":107000,"text":"But nothing, nothing prepared me"},{"time":110000,"text":"for what I was to hear"},{"time":113000,"text":"on the first of July 2008."},{"time":116000,"text":"I heard the word \"carcinoma.\""},{"time":119000,"text":"Yes, breast cancer."},{"time":122000,"text":"As I sat dumbstruck in my doctor's office,"},{"time":127000,"text":"I heard other words:"},{"time":129000,"text":"\"cancer,\" \"stage,\" \"grade.\""},{"time":132000,"text":"Until then, Cancer was the zodiac"},{"time":134000,"text":"sign of my friend,"},{"time":136000,"text":"stage was what I performed on,"},{"time":139000,"text":"and grades were what I got in school."},{"time":144000,"text":"That day, I realized"},{"time":146000,"text":"I had an unwelcome, uninvited,"},{"time":149000,"text":"new life partner."},{"time":152000,"text":"As a dancer,"},{"time":154000,"text":"I know the nine rasas or the navarasas:"},{"time":157000,"text":"anger, valor,"},{"time":159000,"text":"disgust, humor"},{"time":161000,"text":"and fear."},{"time":163000,"text":"I thought I knew what fear was."},{"time":165000,"text":"That day, I learned what fear was."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169000,"text":"Overcome with the enormity of it all"},{"time":172000,"text":"and the complete feeling of loss of control,"},{"time":174000,"text":"I shed copious tears"},{"time":176000,"text":"and asked my dear husband, Jayant."},{"time":179000,"text":"I said, \"Is this it? Is this the end of the road?"},{"time":182000,"text":"Is this the end of my dance?\""},{"time":185000,"text":"And he, the positive soul that he is,"},{"time":188000,"text":"said, \"No, this is just a hiatus,"},{"time":191000,"text":"a hiatus during the treatment,"},{"time":193000,"text":"and you'll get back to doing what you do best.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"I realized then"},{"time":199000,"text":"that I, who thought I had complete control of my life,"},{"time":202000,"text":"had control of only three things:"},{"time":205000,"text":"My thought, my mind --"},{"time":208000,"text":"the images that these thoughts created --"},{"time":210000,"text":"and the action that derived from it."},{"time":213000,"text":"So here I was wallowing"},{"time":215000,"text":"in a vortex of emotions"},{"time":217000,"text":"and depression and what have you,"},{"time":219000,"text":"with the enormity of the situation,"},{"time":222000,"text":"wanting to go to a place of healing, health and happiness."},{"time":226000,"text":"I wanted to go from where I was"},{"time":228000,"text":"to where I wanted to be,"},{"time":230000,"text":"for which I needed something."},{"time":233000,"text":"I needed something that would pull me out of all this."},{"time":236000,"text":"So I dried my tears,"},{"time":238000,"text":"and I declared to the world at large ..."},{"time":241000,"text":"I said, \"Cancer's only one page in my life,"},{"time":244000,"text":"and I will not allow this page to impact the rest of my life.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":248000,"text":"I also declared to the world at large"},{"time":250000,"text":"that I would ride it out,"},{"time":252000,"text":"and I would not allow cancer to ride me."},{"time":254000,"text":"But to go from where I was"},{"time":256000,"text":"to where I wanted to be,"},{"time":258000,"text":"I needed something."},{"time":260000,"text":"I needed an anchor, an image,"},{"time":262000,"text":"a peg"},{"time":264000,"text":"to peg this process on,"},{"time":266000,"text":"so that I could go from there."},{"time":269000,"text":"And I found that in my dance,"},{"time":273000,"text":"my dance, my strength, my energy, my passion,"},{"time":275000,"text":"my very life breath."},{"time":278000,"text":"But it wasn't easy."},{"time":280000,"text":"Believe me, it definitely wasn't easy."},{"time":283000,"text":"How do you keep cheer"},{"time":285000,"text":"when you go from beautiful"},{"time":287000,"text":"to bald in three days?"},{"time":290000,"text":"How do you not despair"},{"time":293000,"text":"when, with the body ravaged by chemotherapy,"},{"time":296000,"text":"climbing a mere flight of stairs was sheer torture,"},{"time":299000,"text":"that to someone like me who could dance for three hours?"},{"time":304000,"text":"How do you not get overwhelmed"},{"time":306000,"text":"by the despair and the misery of it all?"},{"time":309000,"text":"All I wanted to do was curl up and weep."},{"time":312000,"text":"But I kept telling myself fear and tears"},{"time":314000,"text":"are options I did not have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":317000,"text":"So I would drag myself into my dance studio --"},{"time":320000,"text":"body, mind and spirit -- every day into my dance studio,"},{"time":323000,"text":"and learn everything I learned"},{"time":325000,"text":"when I was four, all over again,"},{"time":327000,"text":"reworked, relearned, regrouped."},{"time":330000,"text":"It was excruciatingly painful, but I did it."},{"time":333000,"text":"Difficult."},{"time":336000,"text":"I focused on my mudras,"},{"time":339000,"text":"on the imagery of my dance,"},{"time":341000,"text":"on the poetry and the metaphor"},{"time":343000,"text":"and the philosophy of the dance itself."},{"time":345000,"text":"And slowly, I moved out"},{"time":347000,"text":"of that miserable state of mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351000,"text":"But I needed something else."},{"time":353000,"text":"I needed something to go that extra mile,"},{"time":356000,"text":"and I found it in that metaphor"},{"time":358000,"text":"which I had learned from my mother when I was four."},{"time":361000,"text":"The metaphor of Mahishasura Mardhini,"},{"time":364000,"text":"of Durga."},{"time":366000,"text":"Durga, the mother goddess, the fearless one,"},{"time":369000,"text":"created by the pantheon of Hindu gods."},{"time":372000,"text":"Durga, resplendent, bedecked, beautiful,"},{"time":376000,"text":"her 18 arms"},{"time":378000,"text":"ready for warfare,"},{"time":380000,"text":"as she rode astride her lion"},{"time":383000,"text":"into the battlefield to destroy Mahishasur."},{"time":387000,"text":"Durga, the epitome"},{"time":389000,"text":"of creative feminine energy,"},{"time":391000,"text":"or shakti."},{"time":393000,"text":"Durga, the fearless one."},{"time":395000,"text":"I made that image of Durga"},{"time":397000,"text":"and her every attribute, her every nuance,"},{"time":399000,"text":"my very own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401000,"text":"Powered by the symbology of a myth"},{"time":404000,"text":"and the passion of my training,"},{"time":407000,"text":"I brought laser-sharp focus into my dance,"},{"time":410000,"text":"laser-sharp focus to such an extent"},{"time":412000,"text":"that I danced a few weeks after surgery."},{"time":415000,"text":"I danced through chemo and radiation cycles,"},{"time":418000,"text":"much to the dismay of my oncologist."},{"time":421000,"text":"I danced between chemo and radiation cycles"},{"time":423000,"text":"and badgered him to fit it"},{"time":425000,"text":"to my performing dance schedule."},{"time":430000,"text":"What I had done"},{"time":432000,"text":"is I had tuned out of cancer"},{"time":434000,"text":"and tuned into my dance."},{"time":438000,"text":"Yes, cancer has just been one page in my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443000,"text":"My story"},{"time":445000,"text":"is a story of overcoming setbacks,"},{"time":447000,"text":"obstacles and challenges"},{"time":449000,"text":"that life throws at you."},{"time":451000,"text":"My story is the power of thought."},{"time":454000,"text":"My story is the power of choice."},{"time":457000,"text":"It's the power of focus."},{"time":459000,"text":"It's the power of bringing ourselves"},{"time":462000,"text":"to the attention of something that so animates you,"},{"time":465000,"text":"so moves you,"},{"time":467000,"text":"that something even like cancer becomes insignificant."},{"time":470000,"text":"My story is the power of a metaphor."},{"time":472000,"text":"It's the power of an image."},{"time":474000,"text":"Mine was that of Durga,"},{"time":476000,"text":"Durga the fearless one."},{"time":479000,"text":"She was also called Simhanandini,"},{"time":481000,"text":"the one who rode the lion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485000,"text":"As I ride out,"},{"time":487000,"text":"as I ride my own inner strength,"},{"time":489000,"text":"my own inner resilience,"},{"time":491000,"text":"armed as I am with what medication can provide"},{"time":494000,"text":"and continue treatment,"},{"time":496000,"text":"as I ride out into the battlefield of cancer,"},{"time":498000,"text":"asking my rogue cells to behave,"},{"time":503000,"text":"I want to be known not as a cancer survivor,"},{"time":506000,"text":"but as a cancer conqueror."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508000,"text":"I present to you an excerpt of that work"},{"time":510000,"text":"\"Simhanandini.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":513000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":516000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":909000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}